# VRIN Hybrid RAG SDK v0.2.0

Enterprise-grade Hybrid RAG SDK with optimized knowledge graph traversal and vector search.

## ğŸš€ Features

- âš¡ **Optimized Hybrid RAG** - Combines graph knowledge with vector similarity search
- ğŸ§  **Intelligent Entity Extraction** - AI-powered entity recognition and graph traversal
- ğŸ“Š **Advanced Fact Extraction** - High-confidence fact extraction with scoring
- ğŸ” **Sub-2s Query Response** - Lightning-fast hybrid retrieval performance  
- ğŸ¯ **AI-Powered Summaries** - Natural language answers with cited facts
- ğŸ“ˆ **Enterprise-Ready** - User isolation, authentication, and production scaling

